Comment.val:
Instead of a separate maintenance- ('STAM') , Display- ('DISP') and Report- (RAPP) function the new standard for the maintenanace of data is now is a start-screen displaying essential data in line-mode Empty dataview is allowed) Via Buttons several subfunction are made available.
Add (Toevoegen): To add new data Details: To display the complete record in screen mode. Modify (Wijzigen): To modify an existing record Delete (Verwijderen): To delete an existing record Print: To start a printer selection Transalate (Optional) for data connected to transalations-table ('TABEL_GEGEVENS_VERTAALD)
Typically: the Create/Modify and details function are handled in one subtask. The may situations where it is advisable to separate the function.
See the https://knowledge.able.eu/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=19005551 for autorisation issues. See the mockup-function to emulate rights.
